        "type": "message",
        "text": "Huge fan of this Scott\n\nMy first \"tool for thought\" was opening excel and treating it as a whiteboard – I could just use the arrow keys to get to new locations – I'd have some pages with extra wide cells, some with extra narrow – still the best diary I've ever had\n\nKnotend already has great feel – the simple menus and default font seem just right – example videos are great – the undo is pretty killer – overall :star-struck:",
